Description: Privacy-focused web analytics service
 A lightweight, privacy-focused web analytics service that provides
 real-time insights without tracking personal data. Features include:
  .
  - Simple HTTP API for event ingestion
  - Dashboard for visualizing analytics data
  - SQLite database (no external dependencies)
  - Configurable data retention policies
  - Rate limiting and API key authentication
  - Systemd integration for easy deployment
